<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Trendora Newsletter</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo {
      max-width: 150px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .benefits {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .unsubscribe {
      color: #777;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <img src="https://i.imgur.com/7oTcLHs.png" alt="Trendora Logo" class="logo">
    <h1>Welcome to Trendora Newsletter!</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hello,</p>

    <p>Thank you for subscribing to the Trendora newsletter! We're excited to have you join our community.</p>

    <div class="benefits">
      <p>As a subscriber, you'll be the first to know about:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>New product arrivals</li>
        <li>Exclusive deals and promotions</li>
        <li>Seasonal sales events</li>
        <li>Fashion tips and trends</li>
        <li>Special subscriber-only offers</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p>We'll be sending you updates approximately once a week, so your inbox won't be overwhelmed.</p>

    <p>In the meantime, feel free to check out our latest collections on our website.</p>

    <p>Thank you for your interest in Trendora!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The Trendora Team</p>

    <p class="unsubscribe">If you wish to unsubscribe at any time, simply click the unsubscribe link at the bottom of any newsletter email.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2023 Trendora. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This email was sent to <%= email %> because you subscribed to our newsletter.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
